{
  "id": "adv_card_kkr_14_03",
  "title": "赤崎こころ",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_office-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――ララ達が帰った後",
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 9133.3333412,
          "startTime": 9.1333333412
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_fart-01.m4a",
          "delay": 8033.3333412,
          "startTime": 8.0333333412
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 7733.3333333,
          "startTime": 7.7333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（ララさん達がいたのが嘘だったみたいに静かになったな）\n（こころも最近は大人し――）",
      "startTime": 6.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_03-kkr001.m4a",
      "text": "な、なんて下品な爆音！？　信じられない！\nも、もしかして{user}さん……",
      "startTime": 15.1933332522,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_03-kkr002.m4a",
      "text": "こころ達、可憐なアイドルがいる華やかな事務所を\n悪臭で汚すつもりですかぁ～！？",
      "startTime": 22.6750281196,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "違うっ！　俺はおならなんてしてないぞ！\nほら、椅子にブーブークッションが……",
      "startTime": 28.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "待て。これ、仕掛けたのこころだろ\nこんなことするのはこころぐらいしかいないしな",
      "startTime": 34.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_03-kkr003.m4a",
      "text": "ひ、酷いです！　BIG4のこころを疑うなんて～！\nって、さすがに無理ですよねぇ。バレちゃいましたか～",
      "startTime": 42.515465331,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_03-kkr004.m4a",
      "text": "捨てられた子犬みたいに寂しそうだったのでつい～\nでもブーブークッションってありきたりですよね～",
      "startTime": 51.0821319977,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_03-kkr005.m4a",
      "text": "モモちゃんと考えた悪戯には遠く及びません\n宇宙植物を使った方が面白かったです",
      "startTime": 58.7821330149,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "確か不審者対策にいくつかもらっていたはずだろう\n使ってほしい訳では全くないが、それを使わないのか",
      "startTime": 65.9223256992,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_03-kkr006.m4a",
      "text": "打ち上げの時に使い切っちゃいまして\nもっともらっておけば良かったです～",
      "startTime": 73.3309312264,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "もうないのか。それは一安心だ\nあれはもう二度とごめんだからな……",
      "startTime": 79.9666679382,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_03-kkr007.m4a",
      "text": "あはは、大丈夫ですよ\nしたくても、もう二度と出来ないんですからね",
      "startTime": 85.9361950874,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_03-kkr008.m4a",
      "text": "だってモモちゃんには、も、もう……\nう、うううう……",
      "startTime": 94.5695284287,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "よっぽどこころの方が寂しそうじゃないか\nほら、泣かないでく――",
      "startTime": 101.4000043233,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_03-kkr009.m4a",
      "text": "うう……うう～～～～！！\nむきゃああああ！！　モモちゃんめぇ～！",
      "startTime": 105.8550481573,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "泣くどころか地団駄踏むほどに怒っている！？\nお、落ち着け、モモさんと何があったんだ",
      "startTime": 114.0000017802,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_03-kkr010.m4a",
      "text": "聞いて下さいよー！\nとんでもない事件が打ち上げの後に起きたんです！",
      "startTime": 119.4685061455,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "あ、分かったぞ。計画していたモモさんにする悪戯\n全部失敗したんだろう",
      "startTime": 128.3666684468,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_03-kkr011.m4a",
      "text": "ぶぶー、逆ですよ～！　モモちゃん面白いぐらい\nこころの悪戯に引っかかってくれたんですから！",
      "startTime": 133.9018342098,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_03-kkr012.m4a",
      "text": "ちょっとだけぷりぷり可愛く怒ってましたけど\nすぐに笑って許してくれて……ただその後に……",
      "startTime": 139.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_03-kkr013.m4a",
      "text": "最後の思い出に一緒に寝たいって言ってくれまして\nこころもいいよーって快諾してあげたんです",
      "startTime": 148.9351675432,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_03-kkr014.m4a",
      "text": "でも、部屋で二人っきりになった瞬間\nモモちゃん、こ、こころを押し倒して……",
      "startTime": 156.6018316031,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_03-kkr015.m4a",
      "text": "体中をくすぐってきたんです～！！\nどんなにやめてって言っても、楽しそうに続けて……",
      "startTime": 166.7685008765,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_03-kkr016.m4a",
      "text": "それどころか宇宙植物まで使って縛ってきて！\nあんなとこやこんなとこまでこしょこしょしてきて！",
      "startTime": 174.668502911,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_03-kkr017.m4a",
      "text": "しかも凄い顔で、こころを連れて帰りたいとか\nずっとこうしていたい、可愛いとか言うんですよ！？",
      "startTime": 183.5351736468,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_03-kkr018.m4a",
      "text": "あ、あれは完全に捕食者の目でした！\n鬼の莉央さんよりも恐ろしかったです……",
      "startTime": 191.7351858538,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_03-kkr019.m4a",
      "text": "さすがに命の危機を感じて……ララさんから聞いてた\n弱点の尻尾をぎゅーってしてやったんです！",
      "startTime": 198.4685263079,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_03-kkr020.m4a",
      "text": "そこからは、もうお互い負けじと戦って……\n最後には二人とも力尽きて気絶する形で寝ちゃいました",
      "startTime": 205.5685100239,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "そ、それは……\n壮絶だったな",
      "startTime": 216.0333361308,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_03-kkr021.m4a",
      "text": "うううううっ、消化不良です～！\n最後に最大の悪戯をされちゃいました～",
      "startTime": 221.8885230463,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_03-kkr022.m4a",
      "text": "くぅ、今なら分かります！\nこころの悪戯に面白いぐらい引っかかっていた理由が！",
      "startTime": 228.0551897129,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_03-kkr023.m4a",
      "text": "あれは油断を誘うためだったんですよ！\n最後にこころをはずかしめるための布石だったんです！",
      "startTime": 235.72250938,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_03-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "ずっと二人はどこか似ていると思っていたが\nモモさんの方が一枚上手だったようだな",
      "startTime": 244.1000027974,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_03-kkr024.m4a",
      "text": "悔しいですが、認めざるを得ません\nあれは悪戯の高みに至るプロです……",
      "startTime": 250.868409737,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_03-kkr025.m4a",
      "text": "でもめげませんよ～！\n次会う時が来たら、完全勝利してやります！",
      "startTime": 256.0017430704,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_03-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "次、か。もうないと思っていたが\nそうだな、きっと次もあるよな",
      "startTime": 264.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
